Interface NotifyTriggerBL.FIELDTYPE

  • Enclosing class:
    NotifyTriggerBL

    public static interface NotifyTriggerBL.FIELDTYPE
    Defines the meaning of the "Field" field, relevant only for ACTIONTYPE = EDIT_ISSUE to avoid collision between the issue fieldIDs and budget/cost fieldIDs
